- download Ubuntu Precise Pangolin 12.04.1 Server install ISO 64bit
- create a boot media with unetbootin
- install preseed files:

git clone git@github.com:opinsys/puavo-ltsp.git
cd puavo-ltsp/bootserver/installer
mount /dev/sdb1 /media/usbstick
sh install.sh
umount /dev/sdb1

Then just plug it in, boot and wait until the installation is finished.
